name: New OBJKT (The Expedition, 2021)
description: We ascend and bid farewell - for now. The Expedition was a collection of seven sculptures that required Explorer participation to release. Minted in partnership with the HEN House Discord Server. The New OBJKT was released after Explorers burned 33 fragments from the ruins of its host temple. Holders of the New OBJKT will be eligible for airdrops of future works.
